LOCATION LOCATION - Enjoy unique FRONT & BACK full lake view from this Bellacera Model NESLTED ON Cul de Sac with no thru traffic in amenity filled PGA VERANO.  This 3BR+Den/3.5BA/3CG home boasting charm is tastefully upgraded.  Lake view Gourmet Kitchen features large center Island, granite counter, glass tile backsplash w/ Pot Filler under cabinet lighting, canopy hood, SS upscale appliances, cabinet pull-outs butler's pantry. Other finishes include  IMPACT WINDOWS, diag. tile flooring, crown moulding, double glass lake view  front entry doors, custom window treatments incl plantation shutters, wet bar h/u, designer light fixtures/ceiling fans, Central Vac . LAKE VIEW  Primary Suite has tray ceiling, cust W/I closets, ensuite bath, frame-less glass shower w body faucet, Storage galore Both Guest Suites have ensuite baths, - W/I custom closet in 1. New HWH 2023. Abundance of custom storage in 3 Car garage , attic stairs  attic  lighting and flooring,  garage has plenty of room for a golf cart.

For the Golfer, the cart path leading to PGA Golf Club is right at the beginning of the Street.(PGA Golf Club membership and other memberships available separately.

HOA  includes, lawn care, cable, internet, alarm monitoring, gated manned security gate. The amenity filled community has 27 Pickle Ball courts, tennis courts, walking paths, bocce, 2 gyms 1 
(e-gygm), exercise room and classes,  resistance pool, outdoor resort pool with cabanas, indoor pool, sauna men's and women's locker rooms, hot tubs, card room, library, demonstration kitchen. Plenty of social clubs and planned events , ballroom, outdoor fire pit, fireplace,  BBQ and large patio areas. Something for everyone at Verano.
